<h2>Form olusturma</h2>
Mutlaka <strong>form</strong> etiketinin icinde olmalidir. <br><br>
&lt;form action="https://amazon.de" method="get"><br>
&lt;div><br>
&lt;label for="ad">Isim giriniz&lt;/label><br>
&lt;input type="text" name="isim:" value="adiniz" id="ad"><br>
&lt;/div><br>
&lt;div><br>
&lt;label for="">Mail giriniz&lt;/label><br>
&lt;input type="email" name="email" placeholder="isim"> <br>
&lt;/div> <br>
&lt;button type="submit">Gönder&lt;/button> <br>
&lt;Input type="submit" value="Gönder">&lt;/Input> <br>
&lt;/form> <br><br>

Label eski form oldugu icin yer tasarrufu acisindak kullanilmasi tavsiye edilmez. <br><br>

&lt;input type="text" name="Vorname:" placeholder="Vorname"> <br><br>
<input type="text" name="Vorname:" placeholder="Vorname"> <br>
<input type="email" name="E-mail:" placeholder="E-Mail*" required> <br>
<input type="tel" name="Telefon:" placeholder="Telefon"><br><br>

<strong>pettern</strong> atributu ile telefon no formati ayarlanabilir. <br><br>

eger label deki <strong>for</strong> atributu ile inputtaki <strong>id</strong> ayni ada sahipse 
label in icinde yazan yaziya da tiklandiginda input AKTIF olur. <br><br>

<strong>name</strong> atributu <strong>action</strong> atributunda yazilan adrese giden bilginin 
ayrintisini göstermektedir. <br><br>

<strong>name</strong> ve <strong>value</strong> atributunun birlikte bulunmasi arzu edilir.

eger form daki method yerine <strong>get</strong> yazilirsa bilgiler görünerek gider. <strong>post</strong>
yazilirsa gizliden gider. <br><br>

buton input veya button olarak iki türlü de olusturulabilir. <br><br>

Eger yazi kutusunun icinde bizden istenilen bilgi yazsin denilirse; <br>
<strong>placeholder=""</strong> atributu kullanilmalidir.

<form action="https://amazon.de" method="get">
    <div>
        <label for="ad">Isim giriniz</label>
        <input type="text" name="isim:" value="adiniz" placeholder="isim" id="ad">
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for="">Mail giriniz</label>
        <input type="email" name="email">
    </div>
    <button type="submit">Gönder</button> <br>
    <Input type="submit" value="Gönder"></Input>
</form> <br>


type kismina <strong>number</strong> da girilebilir. <br>
&lt;input type="number"> <br>
&lt;input type="number" name="quantity" min="1" max="5"> <br>
&lt;input type="range" min="0" max="20"> <br>
&lt;input type="date"> <br>
&lt;input type="month"> <br>
&lt;input type="week"> <br>
&lt;input type="datetime-local"> <br>
&lt;input type="time"> <br>
&lt;input type="color"> <br>
&lt;input type="url"> <br>
